{"tid":1327140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髮族遊行改變咗我全家","createTime":"2019-07-17T13:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:37:06.000Z","uid":261132,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f84c71dc5de7c41455f6eed9c5e240c1299bacd9","tid":1327140,"uid":261132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"是咁的，本來我全家都因為最近示威問題大家有各自觀點會嘈一餐，大家食飯果時都唔會出聲，食完就番房上連登。<br />\n<br />\n今日收工一番屋企等食飯果陣，老母出廚房大聲同我老豆講（唔知係咪其實想講我聽）話：喂，你今日有無睇下fb youtube呀，葉德嫺真係好得閒，佢去左個銀髮遊行呀。<br />\n<br />\n正當我想發脾氣話明明人地係為咗香港先企出黎關得閒撚事果一刻，我老母再補多句：佢講果句話後生仔無錯，做得岩，聽完諗番呢排嘅事，有感動到我呀。之後我老豆好冷靜咁講：咁我又唔係盲撐嘅，都識分是非黑白嘅（屌，平時同我嘈話後生仔搞亂晒果陣又唔係咁講？）。<br />\n<br />\n到食飯果陣，兩老問我721係咪會去，叫我小心啲。<br />\n<br />\n我呢餐晚餐好似食咗好耐咁，但我仍然成餐無出過聲，因為我眼淚已經忍唔住咁一直流，流到感覺到自己面容扭曲咗。<br />\n<br />\n想多謝Deanie姐，你拯救咗我屋企！！！<br />\n亦想同各位巴絲講，銀髮遊行真係可以打動到某部份成年人，大家為咗香港，繼續努力，多啲俾其他媒體資訊佢地睇，慢慢佢地都會知道是非對錯。"},{"pid":"5dd75887d671e55469e36b081ed75518cf70ea3a","tid":1327140,"uid":264192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad4d13bc6a66c9d067822e5ab94b263fa74406c","tid":1327140,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:12:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42de617762e24f2317da9e76af6599de5a1c13fa","tid":1327140,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:15:19.000Z","msg":"葉德嫻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951e2336e057d5790959553756e13a29213b0f5d","tid":1327140,"uid":176657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:16:58.000Z","msg":"香港仲有好多明辯是非既老友記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa83bca4cc891bdaffb1d44c3b696a7b48a113fe","tid":1327140,"uid":34415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />deanie姐去足咁多場 小心身體"},{"pid":"ff34feff59391248a9abeca192b451d3a0ee39fd","tid":1327140,"uid":261132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"我都估唔到平時自己講幾多，傳幾多長輩圖都無用，兩老自己睇非tvb外媒體一日就通咗，所以先想同大家分享，好感動，終於全家人有個共識，嘈少餐啦"},{"pid":"8353197bef8a41eaa02acaf077e064689bb8bcdb","tid":1327140,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135a5ac434eafb84c519a7f688f34835eb5e117e","tid":1327140,"uid":253826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zmfhwMB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzmfhwMB.png&h=242c6e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHDi0EY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHDi0EY.png&h=978d7105&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdZNTZ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdZNTZ3.png&h=61870113&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xz1P7j4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXz1P7j4.png&h=090d1b7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"668e13d0fb58f546f2454ebcbfbbfd6ddd964dad","tid":1327140,"uid":181727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}